channel.title: Wont let me put my server up on moparscape list!
channel.description:
I know i put this before but now i've tried a no-ip.info and my ip for my comp and it always says my server is offline when i try to put it up.... I'm able to log in but no one else!!! What do i do?
[URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img338.imageshack.us/img338/7684/rsserverproblem4cm8.jpg[/img][/URL]

item.dc:creator: @zezi111 zezi111
item.description:
@zezi111 wrote:

Make sure you go into your server folder and click runserver.bat make sure that’s open or it wont work and if it still doesn’t work you port-forwarded wrong.
